Motschulsky, 1859a: 154 [primary homonym of 
<taxonomicName class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Amara" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="596" pageNumber="597" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="similata" subSpecies="brunnipes">
